g.title: j4031595650
g.text: Need you to get more gauze

g.title: j4036702486
g.text: Anita got into a box and chewed through some

g.title: j1655593898
g.text: I have no idea who that is, Lettie.

g.title: j1468680543
g.text: My newest corazoncito, my new rat
She is still learning to behave

g.title: j2364707382
g.text: If I see any, I'll grab some.

g.title: j2065499579
g.text: You can go out and get the gauze then, if your rat ate it.

g.title: j1451399433
g.text: I'm curious, why do you keep rats as pets?

g.title: j480112766
g.text: Sí, with all my spare time

g.title: j4236796905
g.text: I don't think I like where this is going. [End.]

g.title: j1750368042
g.text: I want to know why you think I like rats

g.title: j326877362
g.text: Because they're intelligent, affectionate, and playful?

g.title: j969878837
g.text: Because they're often neglected and misunderstood?

g.title: j1274043161
g.text: Lettie? I don't understand the first thing about you. But the rats are cute as hell.

g.title: j41389459
g.text: Didn't grow up with a lot of money as a kid
Rats were easy to keep, mi mamá didn't mind

g.title: j3798256017
g.text: You want to get those bandages?

g.title: j4083881483
g.text: Sure, I'll see what I can do.

g.title: j1514348849
g.text: You can get them, since she's your rat.
